OL,3,CInside the mouse-infested tea room
OL,4,Cclosed down by council
OL,6,FThe owner of a tea room in Stourton
OL,7,Fhas been fined more than #6,000 after
OL,8,Fa council inspection found the
OL,9,Fpremises had an "extensive mouse
OL,10,Finfestation" and other health risks.
OL,12,FOfficers visited the Willow Tree Tea
OL,13,FRooms in South Staffordshire and found
OL,14,F'very poor' conditions - with a lack
OL,15,Fof cleaning, no hot water for food
OL,16,Fhandlers to wash their hands as well
OL,17,Fas the animal infestation throughout
OL,18,Fthe kitchen and storage areas.
