OL,3,CInside the mouse-infested tea room
OL,4,Cclosed down by council
OL,6,FThe council officers serviced a
OL,7,FHygiene Emergency Prohibition Notice,
OL,8,Fwhich immediately closed the business,
OL,9,Fwhich was required to remain closed
OL,10,Funtil the mouse infestation had been
OL,11,Feradicated.
OL,13,FMr Peter McGovern, the owner of Willow
OL,14,FTree Tea Rooms, attended Kidderminster
OL,15,FMagistrates Court on Friday, 6
OL,16,FDecember, where he pleaded guilty to
OL,17,Foffences contrary to Food Safety and
OL,18,FHygiene Regulations.
