OL,6,FHe was ordered to pay #6,122,17 -
OL,7,Fafter an initial fine of #2,00 imposed
OL,8,Fby the judge, victim surcharges of
OL,9,F#800 and prosecution costs of
OL,10,F#3,322.17.
OL,12,FCouncillor Rita Heseltine from South
OL,13,FStaffordshire Council said: "This
OL,14,Fbusiness failed to protect the public
OL,15,Fand did not act promptly on evidence
OL,16,Fof rodent activity within the business.
