OL,3,CInside the mouse-infested tea room
OL,4,Cclosed down by council
OL,6,F"The conditions found by officers were
OL,7,Fan imminent risk to health and a
OL,8,FHygiene Emergency Prohibition Notice
OL,9,Fhad to be served on the business to
OL,10,Fprevent them from trading.
OL,12,F"I am pleased that the court, through
OL,13,Fthe penalties imposed, recognised the
OL,14,Fseriousness of this matter. We would
OL,15,Falways encourage food businesses to
OL,16,Fseek our advice and assistance at the
OL,17,Fearliest opportunity."
